#

Sautéed Pork Loin with Mashed Potatoes and Steamed Vegetables

40 min
$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodDinner

Description

Tender pork loin served with creamy mashed potatoes and colorful steamed vegetables for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • pork loin: 1 pound
  • potatoes: 2 large
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • mixed vegetables (like carrots, broccoli, and bell peppers): 2 cups
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
